00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:41.600
[Amit Varma]: and everything to do with politics. How can we tell if a government is doing a good job?

00:02:41.600 --> 00:02:47.360
[Amit Varma]: One measure is the economy. How can we tell how well the economy is doing? The most common metric

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:52.240
[Amit Varma]: is the GDP. So no wonder there's been so much fighting over it, illustrating what a Greek

